          <div class="eyebrow">
        <a href="/covid-19-pandemic" hreflang="en">COVID-19 Pandemic</a>
      </div>
        <div class="teaser__title">
      <a class="teaser__title-link" href="/covid-19-pandemic/months-virus-biggest-one-day-case-spike-worries-iran" title="Months Into Virus, Biggest One-Day Case Spike Worries Iran"><span>Months Into Virus, Biggest One-Day Case Spike Worries Iran </span>
</a>
    </div>
    <div class="teaser__text">
      As businesses open and people begin to move around more, health experts fear a growing complacency among Iran&#039;s 80 million people may further allow the virus to spread
    </div>
          <div class="teaser__author">
        <div class="teaser__author-image">
          <div>
  
  
